CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1958 , pg. 1 reads: "After Three of Seven Wrecks - These automobiles were among those damaged in seven crashes last week and this week. The wrecks in which these cars were involved occurred in East Liberty, Homewood and the Hill District.  ..Three persons were injured when the auto, center, collided with another in Homewood..."
TitMainTitle: Light colored car with front end and hood damage, letters written into dirt on passenger side door, parked in lot with other automobiles, building in background
